__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 AMM 24-XX-XX-XXX-XXX                     |   Circuit Breaker Locations and Safety Procedures
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 WDM XX-XX-XX (Relevant Wiring Diagram)   |   Electrical interface details for power and control.
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 Ramp Test Set User Manual [MODEL_XYZ]    |   Operating instructions for the specific ramp test equipment.
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 ARINC Specification 716 (or later)       |   Technical characteristics for Airborne VHF Communications Transceiver.
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 Aircraft Logbook                         |   For recording maintenance actions and test results.
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________


